</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Demo trading and multi-exchange bots</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Bitsgap</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Simple Grid and DCA automation</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">TradeSanta</span></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">BitsStrategy may suit users looking for a more managed setup process. Users who want deeper bot control may prefer 3Commas or Bitsgap. Traders who want templates and cloud automation may prefer Cryptohopper. Users who want simple Grid and DCA bots may find TradeSanta easier to test.</span></p>
<h2><b>Features to Evaluate During an AI Trading Bot Free Trial </b></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">A free trial is most useful when users test one clear workflow instead of trying every feature at once.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Good first tests include:</span></p>
<table>
