<td><b>Feature</b></td>
<td><b>Why It Matters</b></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Grid Bot</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Shows how automated range trading works</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">DCA Bot</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Helps users understand staged entries</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
