<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Lets users test without live funds</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Stop Loss</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Shows how exit rules work</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Take Profit</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Helps users understand target-based exits</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
