<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Shows how the bot actually behaves</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Strategy Templates</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Makes setup faster for beginners</span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Dashboard Reports</span></td>
<td><span style="font-weight: 400;">Helps users track bot activity clearly</span></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The goal of a free trial is not to master every strategy immediately. The goal is to understand how the bot reacts to market movement, how orders are placed, and whether the platform fits the user’s trading style.</span></p>
<h2><b>FAQ</b></h2>
<h3><b>How to Compare Free AI Trading Bots in 2026 </b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">BitsStrategy is useful for users who want a managed AI trading workflow. 3Commas, Cryptohopper, Bitsgap, and TradeSanta are stronger for users who want to test configurable crypto trading bots.</span></p>
<h3><b>Which automated trading platform offers a free trial?</b></h3>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">3Commas offers a 7-day free trial, Bitsgap offers a 7-day PRO trial, and TradeSanta offers a 3-day free trial. Cryptohopper offers a free start option and has promoted a 3-day trial through its app listing.</span></p>
